<li><a href="http://www.join.uni-muenster.de/Dokumente/drafts/draft-bhatia-manral-diff-isis-ospf-01.txt" class="external text" title="http://www.join.uni-muenster.de/Dokumente/drafts/draft-bhatia-manral-diff-isis-ospf-01.txt" rel="nofollow">IS-IS and OSPF difference discussion</a> (Vishwas Manral, Manav bhatia and Yasuhiro Ohara)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ict.tuwien.ac.at/skripten/datenkomm/infobase/L41-OSPF_Fundamentals_v4-5.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.ict.tuwien.ac.at/skripten/datenkomm/infobase/L41-OSPF_Fundamentals_v4-5.pdf" rel="nofollow">Data Communication Lectures of Manfred Lindner - Part OSPF Fundamentals</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ict.tuwien.ac.at/skripten/datenkomm/infobase/L42-OSPF_Advanced_v4-4.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.ict.tuwien.ac.at/skripten/datenkomm/infobase/L42-OSPF_Advanced_v4-4.pdf" rel="nofollow">Data Communication Lectures of Manfred Lindner - Part OSPF Areas</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.tcpipguide.com/free/t_OpenShortestPathFirstOSPF.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.tcpipguide.com/free/t_OpenShortestPathFirstOSPF.htm" rel="nofollow">TCP/IP Guide - OSPF</a></li>
</ul>


